## Dashboard [/Dashboards/{Id}]
### Update a dashboard [PUT]
+ Parameters
    + Id (required, string, `8169134f-ad61-4e0b-a7d8-d143541b6a94`) ... UUID of the Dashboard to perform action with. Has example value.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Body
    
            {
                "Name": "Australian IT Specialists",
                "Widgets": [{
                    "Report": "6103395f-20b5-41fb-9650-03b0ca50cce5",
                    "Type": "same-incumbent-movements",
                    "ViewFilteredBy": "job-family"
                },{
                    "Report": "65c33eb6-df2a-4d68-a6e8-7130800ddcbf",
                    "Type": "same-incumbent-movements",
                    "ViewFilteredBy": "organisation-size"
                }]
            }
            
    + Schema
            
            {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                    "Name": {
                        "type": "string"
                    }, {
                    "Widgets": [
                        "type": "array"
                        "items": {
                            "type": "object",
                            "title": "Widget",
                            "properties": {
                                "Report": {
                                    "type": "string"
                                },
                                "Type": {
                                    "type": "string"
                                },
                                "ViewFilteredBy": {
                                    "type": "string"
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                },
                "required": ["Name"]
            }


+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body
    
            {
            }

