+ Parameters
    + Id (required, string, `8169134f-ad61-4e0b-a7d8-d143541b6a94`) ... UUID of the Dashboard to perform action with. Has example value.

+ Response 204

+ Response 404 (application/json)

    + Body
    
            {
                "ResponseStatus": {
                    "ErrorCode": "NotFound",
                    "Message": "No dashboard was found by this Id"
                }
            }



# Group Notes
Notes related resources of the **Notes API**

## Slides Collection [/slides]
### List all Slides [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [{
          "id": 1, "title": "Jogging in park"
        }, {
          "id": 2, "title": "Pick-up posters from post-office"
        }]

### Create a Slide [POST]
+ Request (application/json)

        { "title": "Buy cheese and bread for breakfast." }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        { "id": 3, "title": "Buy cheese and bread for breakfast." }

## Note [/slides/{id}]
A single Note object with all its details

+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Slide to perform action with. Has example value.

### Retrieve a Slide [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Header

            X-My-Header: The Value

    + Body

            { "id": 2, "title": "Pick-up posters from post-office" }

### Remove a Slide [DELETE]
+ Response 204
